parsed.explanation: Corrected four malformed unicode character sequences which likely resulted from transcription errors (e.g., 'frantz\u221a\u2202sisch' to 'frantzösisch'). Restructured the XML to correctly represent the list of books; separated two titles ('Schweitzer- Chronick' and 'Reich der Todten') into distinct <BIBL> elements, as they were improperly nested. Added a new <DESCRIPTION> tag to semantically contain the concluding text about the sale of the books. Added a comma to improve grammatical structure of the list.
